dataList.content: ...The group remained consistently noisy until the moment we arrived.
Only in tranquility can art bloom in its full grace...

dataList.title: K Corp. Laboratory
dataList.content: There's always gonna be a snobby jerk on any team.
I must agree. I can't tell if they're here to handle a request or hang out... They loosen up too easily...

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: If there's one fortunate thing, however, it's that we won't encounter any Abnormalities here.
<Why does this person keep talking to me?>

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: To tell you the truth, the first encounter with Abnormalities was a series of shocking revelations.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: It was hybrid, so to speak. I wouldn't have been able to conceive such a concept as developing a new source of energy from the human subconscious.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: I believe that the so widespread and standard, hm, what was it again... right, the age of humanity is coming to an end. Now is the age of the superior minds. Not too many have realized this with their hearts yet.

dataList.title: K Corp. Dept. of Food Resource Development
dataList.content: You have no idea how glad I was to have you on board.
<...Some one-sided conversation that was... Much worse than the ones I have with Vergilius.>
Was it even a conversation if one of us never communicated their thoughts to the other?
